Convert OpenVPN Access Server to MySQL Backend
Install MySQL/MariaDB if it is not already installed
sudo apt install mariadb-server
Log into OpenVPN Access Server
Click Tools > DB Convert in the left navigation
Enter the root MySQL password
Click the DB Convert button
Wait for the process to complete
Click the Restart button
Further reading: https://openvpn.net/vpn-server-resources/configuration-database-management-and-backups/
